data.description: Imagine enjoying your morning coffee on the charming screened porch, as the kids or pets play in the spacious backyard. Inside, sun pours through expansive windows, illuminating hardwood floors that shine from years of love and life. The kitchen gleams with recent modern updates, seamlessly blending form and function for easy entertaining. Upstairs, updated bathrooms and cozy bedrooms create a retreat for relaxation and recharging. The basement is full of potential and possibility as it waits to be transformed into an in-law suite or rental to help pay the mortgage. Located on a quiet street near parks and schools, this move-in ready 4BR/2BA colonial provides a solid foundation and room to grow. Come see today and make new memories in a home that's ready for you.
